*.log

# Scratch state only, per throughline's own documented commit policy (README
# "Commit policy"): HANDOFF.md and logs/ ARE meant to be committed - this repo
# now dogfoods itself via THROUGHLINE_DATA_DIR=.agent/handoff, so its own
# HANDOFF.md is tracked like any consuming project's would be.
.claude/throughline/buffer/
.claude/throughline/.capture-errors
.agent/handoff/buffer/
.agent/handoff/.capture-errors
